            <span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glStencilOp</span></span>,
            <span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glStencilOpSeparate</span></span>
        </p></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="id4768609"></a><h2>Copyright</h2><p>
